text: Guadalupe Reyes is a Mexican comedy film directed by Salvador Espinosa, from a screenplay by Erik Zuckermann, Harald Rumpler, and Marcos Bucay. The film stars Juan Pablo Medina and Martín Altomaro, alongside Begoña Narváez, María de la Fuente, Paco Rueda, Memo Villegas, Salvador Zerboni, Roberto Duarte, Tato Alexander, Juan Carlos Colombo, Ofelia Medina, Mauricio Isaac, Arap Bethke, and Emiliano Zurita. The film premiered on 29 November 2019 in Mexico. == Cast == * Juan Pablo Medina * Martín Altomaro * Begoña Narváez * María de la Fuente * Paco Rueda * Memo Villegas * Salvador Zerboni * Roberto Duarte * Tato Alexander * Juan Carlos Colombo * Ofelia Medina * Mauricio Isaac * Arap Bethke * Emiliano Zurita == References == Category:2019 films
